726553f-a.title: Queens: Farmers Boulevard - 140th Avenue
726553f-a.text:
Farmers Boulevard, west side, south of One Hundred Fortieth Ave.
(Himbie Street), showing the Daniel Murray Jr. house of 1891. Other
owners were the Stanton Estate 1909, and Robert Murray in 1913.
September 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

726552f-a.title: Queens: Farmers Boulevard - 139th Avenue
726552f-a.text:
Farmers Boulevard, west side, between 139th Road (right) and
140th Ave. (left), showing the Nicholas Hendrickson house of 1891.
September 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
